title: Cyprus Motor Vehicle Registrations
description: Car Registrations in Cyprus decreased to 2481 in October from 3412 in September of 2022. Car Registrations in Cyprus averaged 3208.12  from 1991 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 7077  in July of 2008 and a record low of 3  in September of 2014. This page provides - Cyprus Car Registrations - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistical Service of the Republic of Cyprus
